name: 大卫·密歇根
introduction: David Michigan is a celebrity life and fitness trainer, model and actor specialized in mind techniques.He has Native American origins, and was born in Paris on the 11th February 1989.More than 9 million people are following his advice on social media.He mainly helps people to lose weight, burn fat and gain muscle. To do it, in addition to hypnosis and self-hypnosis sessions, David Michigan offers personalized nutrition and training programs so that people can quickly get the body of their dream while possessing a powerful mind.
